snippet.title: Retro City Rampage™ DX - 2014 Launch Trailer [PC, Mac, PS4, PS3, VITA, Xbox 360, Wii, 3DS]
snippet.description: Retro City Rampage: DX, a beefed up remastered version of the original game is coming this November to Steam (PC/Mac), PlayStation®4, PlayStation®3, PS Vita, Xbox 360, Nintendo 3DS™ and Wii. See what gives it the 'DX'! -- http://RetroCityRampage.com -- @RetroCR on Twitter
